DESCRIPTION:<b>Saturday\, April 25th\, 10am</b> departure at the Armdale Ro
 undabout.  Refreshments and sociables at the Armview Restaurant upon our re
 turn.<br><br>60km group ride departing from the Armdale Roundabout and head
 ing out St. Margarets Bay Road to Tantallon where we will turn up the 213 t
 o Hammonds Plains Road and back in toward the city along Kearney Lake Road\
 , Dunbrack St and we'll add in a final loop through Spryfield to arrive bac
 k in Armdale.<br><br><b>Current membership in Cycling Nova Scotia is requir
 ed.</b>  Membership in Randonneurs NS is optional for first timers.  We exp
 ect riders to be self-sufficient\, have some experience road riding\, and t
 o be comfortable with vehicle traffic.  We can tell you all about the club
 over post-ride refreshments.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T172839Z
LOCATION:Armdale Roundabout\, Halifax\, NS\, Canada
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Randonneurs Nova Scotia: 60km ride
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
