DESCRIPTION:<p>Know your rights\, ride with confidence! This essential work
 shop provides cyclists with crucial legal knowledge to navigate the roads s
 afely and handle incidents effectively.</p><p><strong>When:</strong> Thursd
 ay\, August 7th | 5PM to 6:30PM<br><strong>Facilitator:</strong> Wagners La
 w Firm</p><p><strong>Workshop Topics:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Road Righ
 ts &amp\; Responsibilities</strong> - Understanding your legal rights as a
 cyclist</li><li><strong>Motorist Interactions</strong> - How to navigate ch
 allenging situations with drivers</li><li><strong>Accident Protocols</stron
 g> - Essential steps to take immediately following an incident</li><li><str
 ong>Evidence Collection</strong> - What to document and how to protect your
 self</li><li><strong>Insurance Claims</strong> - Understanding the claims p
 rocess and your coverage</li><li><strong>Legal Representation</strong> - Wh
 en and how to seek professional help</li><li><strong>Traffic Laws</strong>
 - Cyclist-specific regulations and liability issues</li><li><strong>Prevent
 ion &amp\; Protection</strong> - Strategies to safeguard yourself before in
 cidents occur</li></ul><p><strong>Perfect For:</strong></p><ul><li>Daily co
 mmuters and recreational cyclists</li><li>Anyone wanting to understand thei
 r legal rights on the road</li><li>Cyclists seeking confidence in traffic s
 ituations</li><li>Those who want to be prepared for potential incidents</li
 ></ul><p><strong>What You'll Gain:</strong></p><ul><li>Clear understanding
 of cyclist rights and responsibilities</li><li>Practical knowledge for hand
 ling accidents and insurance claims</li><li>Confidence to navigate complex
 traffic situations</li><li>Professional insights from experienced legal pra
 ctitioners</li></ul><p><b>Register: </b><a href="http://cyclehalifax.ca/leg
 al-workshop" target="_blank">http://cyclehalifax.ca/legal-workshop</a></p>\
 n\nÜber Google Meet teilnehmen: https://meet.google.com/kmo-tqyk-sov\nOder
 telefonisch: (CA) +1 587-688-0182 PIN: 748656711#\nWeitere Telefonnummern:
 https://tel.meet/kmo-tqyk-sov?pin=1484156759873&hs=7\n\nWeitere Information
 en zu Meet: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
