 /cyclehalifax.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=17dcf1fd4f5c6998288f8aec7&a
 mp\;id=60c79eb76d&amp\;e=e19709ad70" target="_blank">signup here</a>. Volun
 teers in previous years have remarked on how much fun it was. No experience
