DESCRIPTION:<p>Join a collaborative community meetup featuring <b>Bike Part
 y</b>\, <b>Coffee Outside Halifax</b>\, <b>Halifax Cycles</b>\, and the <b>
 Halifax Cycling Coalition (HCC)</b>! This Sunday morning gathering brings t
 ogether several local cycling groups for a casual ride and social.</p><p>Th
 e event kicks off at 10:00 AM with a 30-minute\, party-pace group ride that
  starts and ends at the Oval. Following the ride at 10:30 AM\, we’ll transi
 tion into a special weekend edition of Coffee Outside. Jenna from Halifax C
 ycles will be there with demo bikes to try out\, along with prizes and hot
 chocolate for everyone to enjoy. We’ll be doing a prize draw at 10:45 AM fo
 r anyone joining the ride or the meetup. Bring your bike and a mug\, and co
 me hang out!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260129T183118Z
LOCATION:Emera Oval\, 5775 Cogswell St\, Halifax\, NS B3K 4B2\, Canada
