  Approximately 1 - 1.5 hours</p><p>Route Details:</p><p>Distance: 10KM tota
 l<br>Starting/Ending Point: <b>Emera Oval at Halifax Commons<br></b>Route:
 Mostly easy ride between downtown Halifax and Point Pleasant Park via the p
 eninsula’s cycling paths and Point Pleasant’s bike trails.</p><p>Waiver req
 uired. Link in Bio or kindly visit <a href="https://cyclehalifax.ca/waiver"
  target="_blank"><u>https://cyclehalifax.ca/waiver</u></a></p>
