 ook forward to it. We usually have over 200 riders. We’ll have refreshments
  and prizes\, and music.<br><br>This is a family-friendly\, joyous event —
 don’t miss it!<br><br><b>When</b> 📅: Saturday\, November 8 at 6 PM<br><br>
 <b>Where📍: </b>Dal Bike Centre (Regroup at Halifax Commons Oval)<br><br><b
