 https://www.instagram.com/cyclehalifax/" target="_blank"><u><u>Instagram</u
 ></u></a> and <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/cyclehalifax.ca" target="_b
 lank"><u><u>Bluesky</u></u></a> and the <a href="https://cyclehalifax.ca/ev
 ents/" target="_blank"><u><u>HCC Calendar.</u></u></a><br><br><b>NB: A <a h
 ref="https://cyclehalifax.ca/waiver/" target="_blank">waiver</a> (required
 once per year) must be completed to participate in this event.</b><br><b>Da
 lhousie also requires a separate <a href="https://www.bouncelife.com/events
 /68f65fbf88ea7f13628898df" target="_blank">waiver</a> signed because we are
  using their premises. </b>
