DESCRIPTION:<p>Kick off your summer cycling season with our Ride Into Summe
 r! event - a beautiful journey along the Chain of Lakes Trail that's perfec
 t for cyclists of all abilities.</p><br><p><b>When</b>: Saturday\, July 5 a
 t 8:30 AM</p><p><b>Ride Start</b>: 9:00 AM</p><p><b>Duration</b>: Approxima
 tely 2 hours (including cafe stop)</p><br><p><b>Route Details:</b></p><p><b
 >Distance</b>: 9KM total (4.5KM each way)</p><p><b>Starting Point</b>: Entr
 ance of Ashburn Golf Club</p><p><b>Destination</b>: 5K Cafe and back</p><p>
 <b>Terrain</b>: Scenic trail suitable for all skill levels</p><p><b>What's
 Included:</b></p><p></p><ul><li>🚴‍♂️ Guided group ride with experienced le
 aders</li><li>☕ Refreshment break at the popular 5K Cafe</li><li>🏃‍♀️ Grou
 p stretch exercises to start and finish</li><li>👥 Volunteer sweeps to ensu
