DESCRIPTION:<br>Join us at the Oval for a pre-season gathering: our second
 annual Spring Social! We’ll have hot cocoa\, snacks and ride laps on the ov
 al to help keep us warm. We’ve invited so many of our bike friends along fo
 r some great activities:<br><ul><li>cargo bike show &amp\; tell</li><li>e-b
 ike test rides with Halifax Cycles</li><li>stuff-a-bike with Bike Brigade H
 alifax: bring food items for our community fridges</li><li>bike checks and
 minor repairs with the Ecology Action Centre's pop-up bike hub</li></ul>Ple
 ase note\, the oval is not officially open for the season until June\, so t
 here will be no rentals or washrooms available on site for this event.<br>F
 ull details at: <a href="https://hfx.bike/kidical-mass/rides/2026/ride-apri
 l-18/" target="_blank">https://hfx.bike/kidical-mass/<wbr />rides/2026/ride
 -april-18/</a><br>Rain date: Sunday April 19 at 3:00pm
LAST-MODIFIED:20260326T144541Z
LOCATION:Emera Oval\, 5775 Cogswell St\, Halifax\, NS B3K 4B2\, Canada
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kidical Mass Halifax Spring Social
TRANSP:OPAQUE
