DESCRIPTION:<br>Spring "Snack &amp\; Swap" Social<br>4-6pm at Bike Again - 
 5664 Charles St\, Halifax<br><br><i>New to TMC or riding in Kjipuktuk? </i>
 <i>Come hang out at @bikeagainhfx from 4–6pm on Sunday the 12th and get to
 know TMC's programs and pals! We’ll swap snacks (we’ll have lots\, but feel
  free to bring a favourite to share)\, winter adventure stories\, clothes\,
  and bike gear or parts (anything goes). We’ll also share a bit about what
 TMC has in store for 2025. </i><i><b>TMC is a space is for women\, trans\,
 and gender-diverse folks. </b>We think whatever bike and experience level y
 ou have are awesome. See you there!</i>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T172822Z
LOCATION:Bike Again!\, 5664 Charles St\, Halifax\, NS B3K 1K4\, Canada
