DESCRIPTION:<p>Start your Sunday with a relaxing Sunday Morning Cruise - a
 gentle 8KM neighborhood tour that's perfect for cyclists of all abilities</
 p><p>When: Sunday\, July 20 at 8:30 AM<br>Ride Start: 9:00 AM<br>Duration:
 Approximately 2 hours</p><p><b>Route Details:</b></p><ul><li><p>Distance: 8
 KM total</p></li><li><p>Difficulty: Easy - suitable for all skill levels</p
 ></li><li><p>Starting/Ending Point: Emera Oval</p></li><li><p>Route: Neighb
 orhood tour via Halifax Common\, Almon Street\, Geldert Street\, Coburg Roa
 d\, Vernon Street and back to the Oval</p></li><li><p>Terrain:  HRM's desig
 nated cycling roads</p></li></ul><p><b>What's Included:</b></p><ul><li><p>
 🚴‍♀️ Guided easy-paced ride perfect for new cyclists</p></li><li><p>👥 Vol
 unteer sweeps ensuring no one gets left behind</p></li><li><p>🌟 Supportive
 \, no-drop group atmosphere</p></li></ul><p><b>Perfect For:</b></p><ul><li>
 <p>New cyclists building confidence</p></li><li><p>Anyone wanting a relaxed
  Sunday morning activity</p></li><li><p>Families with older children/teens<
 /p></li><li><p>Social cyclists looking to explore neighborhoods</p></li><li
 ><p>Those seeking a supportive\, beginner-friendly group</p></li></ul><p><b
 >What to Bring:</b></p><ul><li><p>Your bike and helmet (mandatory)</p></li>
 <li><p>Water bottle</p></li><li><p>Comfortable cycling clothes</p></li><li>
 <p>Camera for neighborhood photo opportunities</p></li><li><p>Positive atti
 tude and ready to have fun!</p></li></ul><p><b>Route Map</b>: <a href="http
 s://ridewithgps.com/routes/51390712" target="_blank"><u>https://ridewithgps
 .com/routes/51390712</u></a></p><p>Registration and waiver required. Kindly
  visit <a href="https://cyclehalifax.ca/summer-rides" target="_blank"><u>ht
 tps://cyclehalifax.ca/summer-rides</u></a></p><br><p><i>Weather permitting.
  Event updates will be posted 24 hours prior if conditions require changes.
 </i></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250703T135019Z
LOCATION:Emera Oval\, 5775 Cogswell St\, Halifax\, NS B3K 4B2\, Canada
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Sunday Morning Cruise
